name: grape-electron
description: An experimental (but functional) Grape desktop client for Windows / OS X / Linux

releases.name: Release 2.10.0
releases.body:
- Windows: use * for auto app id generation, fix manufacturer field
- Fix MAS signed release build
- Create dev id signed release build for local distribution
- Move docs from the wiki to the docs dir

### Fixes
- Avoid multiple tray icons being created #23 
- Flashing taskbar not working on windows 10 #22 
- Logging on windows #21
- Redirect to the login page when lastUrl info loading fails ubergrape/grape-web-client#244
